<h2><a id=3D"NAME" href=3D"https://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man3/errno.3.ht=
ml#NAME"></a>NAME  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href=3D"https://man7.org/=
linux/man-pages/man3/errno.3.html#top_of_page"><span class=3D"top-link">top=
</span></a></h2><pre>       errno - number of last error
</pre>
